# room-booking — agent context

Before non-trivial edits, read **`AGENTS.md`** (agent memory) and **`README.md`** (human-oriented setup and auth).

- **Auth**: Better Auth + Keycloak; SQLite `data/auth.db`; handler `app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts`; gate `middleware.ts`; API guard `lib/require-session.ts`.
- **Bookings**: `data/bookings.json`, `lib/db.ts`, routes under `app/api/bookings/`.
- **Env**: `.env.example` — `BETTER_AUTH_*`, `KEYCLOAK_*`; Keycloak callback `{BETTER_AUTH_URL}/api/auth/oauth2/callback/keycloak`.

When changing auth or session behavior, update **`AGENTS.md`** and **`README.md`** if contracts or paths change.
